thread-pool provides header-only thread pool for parallel task execution.

Usage:
    find_package(thread-pool CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE thread-pool::thread-pool)

Example:
    #include <thread-pool/thread_pool.hpp>
    tp::thread_pool pool(4);
    auto future = pool.enqueue([](int a, int b) { return a + b; }, 1, 2);
    int result = future.get();
